      • PokerSquaresPointSystem

        public PokerSquaresPointSystem(int[] scores)
        Create a point system given an array of hand scores. The score at index n corresponds to the score for hand classification number n. These will be truncated to be between the minimum and maximum allowable hand scores.
        Parameters:
        scores - given hand scores
